# Sanity Studio (`studio-simonask.io`)

## Layout

- Config: `sanity.config.ts` — structure, presentation, vision plugins
- Schema: `schemaTypes/` (register in `schemaTypes/index.ts`)
- Custom desk: `structure.ts`
- Presentation resolve: `presentation/resolve.ts`
- Env: `env.ts` — project ID and dataset from env vars

## Content model

- Document type `post`: title, slug, publishedAt, image, body (portable text blocks)
- Slugs drive routes on the site: `nextjs-simonask.io/src/app/[slug]/page.tsx`

## Preview

Presentation tool points at the Next app (`SANITY_STUDIO_PREVIEW_ORIGIN`, default `http://localhost:3000`). Draft mode endpoints: `/api/draft-mode/enable` and `/disable` on the Next app.

## Conventions

- Match existing Prettier settings in `package.json` (single quotes, no semis)
- After schema changes: update GROQ in `nextjs-simonask.io/src/sanity/queries.ts` and any TypeScript that depends on fields

More detail: `memories/sanity-conventions.md` and `studio-simonask.io/README.md`
